// Limite depuis le webhook si dispo, sinon défaut 10, toujours 1-50
let limit = 10;
const summaryRecipient = 'ouat.abou34@outlook.fr';
try {
  const allItems = $input.all();
  for (const item of allItems) {
    const bodyLimit = item.json?.body?.limit;
    if (bodyLimit !== undefined && bodyLimit !== null) {
      const parsed = parseInt(String(bodyLimit), 10);
      if (!isNaN(parsed)) limit = Math.max(1, Math.min(50, parsed));
      break;
    }
  }
} catch(e) { /* trigger sans body — valeur par défaut */ }
return [{ json: { maxEmails: limit, summaryRecipient, openAiModel: 'gpt-4o-mini', lookbackHours: 8 } }];

const cfg = $('Configuration MVP').first().json;
const messages = (items[0].json.value || items[0].json.error ? [] : []).concat(items[0].json.value || []);
const excludedSenderFragments = [
  'no-reply', 'noreply', 'newsletter', 'notification', 'notifications',
  'marketing', 'facebookmail', 'linkedin', 'microsoft-noreply'
];
const excludedSubjectFragments = [
  'newsletter', 'desabonnement', 'désabonnement', 'promotion',
  'notification automatique', 'alerte automatique', 'absence du bureau', 'automatic reply'
];
const cutoff = new Date(Date.now() - Number(cfg.lookbackHours || 8) * 60 * 60 * 1000);
const prepared = [];
const skipped = [];
for (const m of messages) {
  const categories = Array.isArray(m.categories) ? m.categories : [];
  const sender = (m.from?.emailAddress?.address || '').toLowerCase();
  const senderName = m.from?.emailAddress?.name || '';
  const subject = m.subject || '(sans objet)';
  const subjectLower = subject.toLowerCase();
  const receivedAt = new Date(m.receivedDateTime);
  const alreadyProcessed = categories.includes('IA - Traite') || categories.includes('IA - Exclu');
  const excludedBySender = excludedSenderFragments.some(x => sender.includes(x));
  const excludedBySubject = excludedSubjectFragments.some(x => subjectLower.includes(x));
  const tooOld = Number.isFinite(receivedAt.getTime()) && receivedAt < cutoff;
  if (alreadyProcessed || excludedBySender || excludedBySubject || tooOld) {
    skipped.push({
      id: m.id, subject, sender,
      reason: alreadyProcessed ? 'deja_traite' : excludedBySender ? 'expediteur_exclu' : excludedBySubject ? 'objet_exclu' : 'trop_ancien'
    });
    continue;
  }
  const bodyText = (m.body?.content || m.bodyPreview || '')
    .replace(/<[^>]+>/g, ' ')
    .replace(/\s+/g, ' ')
    .trim()
    .slice(0, 4000);
  prepared.push({
    id: m.id, subject, sender, senderName,
    receivedDateTime: m.receivedDateTime,
    importance: m.importance, categories,
    hasAttachments: Boolean(m.hasAttachments),
    webLink: m.webLink, bodyText
  });
}
return [{ json: { emails: prepared, skipped, no_emails: prepared.length === 0, runAt: new Date().toISOString() } }];

